examineProject(uint48).details: . The function examine project is used to approve/reject a project

invest(uint48).details: . Function responsible for investors to invest in a project of their choice

params._proposalId: . proposal id of project requesting for funding

leaveDAO().details: . Function responsible for leaving the DAO

pauseProposal().details: . Function pause proposal is used to prevent excessive project proposals

proposeProject(string,uint256,uint256,ad.details: . Function responsible for taking project proposal before, it's being moved to the dao for invedtors

params._equityOffering: . amount of equity offering for that funding
params._fundingRequest: . amount requesting for funding in dollars
params._urlToStore: . url to the storage location of the project proposal overview

setAcceptanceFee(uint128).details: . function responsible to set acceptance fee

params._acceptance: . New acceptance fee to be set

takeProfitInFTM(address,uint256,address,.details: . The function is used to convert token to FTM.

params._amount: . amount intending to swap for FTM
params._amountOutMin: . this should be set to zero if _datafeed is filled. it is used in case  There's no _datafeed
params._dataFeed: . oracle price feed, if any, else null address should be used
params._token: . address of equity offered (token to change)

takeProfitInStable(address,address,uint2.details: . The function is used to convert token to stable token.

params._amount: . amount intending to swap to stable token
params._amountOutMin: . this should be set to zero if _datafeed is filled. it is used in case  There's no _datafeed
params._dataFeed: . oracle price feed, if any, else null address should be used
params._token: . address of equity offered (token to change)

examineProject(uint48).notice: . This function can only be called by the nominated admins

invest(uint48).notice: . This function can only be called by investors

leaveDAO().notice: . When an investor decides to leave the DAO, access ticket is burnt and only 50% of the amount used to join the DAO is refunded.

pauseProposal().notice: . This can only be called by the admin

proposeProject(string,uint256,uint256,ad.notice: . Any body can call this function to propose a project. Project can only be proposed once in a week

takeProfitInFTM(address,uint256,address,.notice: . This function can only be called by an admin. It is used to take profit  by converting equity offered to FTM, to grow VENDAO treasury.

takeProfitInStable(address,address,uint2.notice: . This function can only be called by an admin. It is used to take profit  by converting equity offered to stable token, to grow VENDAO treasury.
